#### PR Classification
Bug fix

#### PR Summary
This pull request resolves a build error by removing the `__init` attribute from a function declaration.
- `include/linux/heki.h`: Removed `__init` attribute from `heki_store_blacklist_raw_hashes` function declaration.
- `virt/heki/module.c`: Removed `__init` attribute from `heki_store_blacklist_raw_hashes` function definition.
